----------------------------------------------------------------------

This project contains documentation and visual assets derived from
materials of the Peking University Hiking Association
(北京大学学生徒步越野协会). These materials include (but are not
limited to):

  - references/handbook.md — excerpts and summaries of the
    Association's Leader Handbook
  - references/leader-handbook-full.md — redacted version of the
    Association's Leader Handbook (2026.4.20 edition)
  - assets/徒协logo.png, assets/徒协logo横版.png — Association logo
  - assets/路线分级1.png, assets/路线分级2.png — Association's
    published route grading standard
  - Route grading formulas, defaults, and field specifications

